i used to have this :

{
  "status": "INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR",
  "message": "Invalid IBAN format: DE4325050180000019880",
  "errorCode": "OLKY_INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR",
  "timestamp": "2025-11-17T13:52:52.741061713"
